<p>There are the people who contribute content, and there are the people who maintain it. The former doesn&#8217;t know the intimate details of the wiki&#8217;s features. The latter does, and will sometimes leave snippy comments about the lack of this as they make it conform to the spec.</p>

<p>The mindset is the same, whatever wikipedia-type place it&#8217;s found on. Even in ones dedicated to misinformation and gossip.</p>

