<p>It&#8217;s not the first time in the history of mankind that a Great Thing is taken over by &#8220;admins&#8221; who don&#8217;t understand much of the Initial Idea, but who understand very well how to benefit of it. Hierarchies, structures and rules prevent any further progress and the Great Thing converts into a Serious Thing, that uses the Initial Idea only as a marketing tool.</p>

